commit.message: Update GitHub Action workflows for new runner
Update to new curl API for libcurl >= 7.85.0

We can not launch terminal browser because it will interfere with
getchar() waiting approach.

Prevent overflow when copying data from ENV
Prevent buffer overflow when building request data

Fix time-of-check time-of-use race condition

Permission checking/setting shall be before opening a file.
Do not perform void pointer arithmetics

Fix invalid signature error when debug is enabled

Since commit a1f9f37 it was impossible to scrobble when cmusfm was
configure with debug enabled. It was caused by the "safety" feature
which removes session key from debug output. Unfortunately, session
key was also removed from POST payload.
